# Ignore everything
*

# Allow root metadata
!.gitignore
!README.md
!LICENSE

# Allow GitHub/Website folders
!.github/
!.github/**
!Website/
!Website/**

# Allow parent Packages folder itself (so Git can descend)
!Packages/

# Allow only the specific package and its contents
!Packages/tech.azuki.vrc-avatar-system/
!Packages/tech.azuki.vrc-avatar-system/**